Photogrammetry (攝影測量)


Remote Sensing (遙感探測)


Radargrammetry (雷達測量)


Computer Vision (計算機視覺)


Image Processing (影像處理)


Image Recognition (圖像識別)


Image Reasoning (影像推理)


Cloud Theory (雲理論)


Signal Processing (訊號處理)


Data Mining (資料探勘)


Automated Image Measurement (自動化影像量測)


Surveying (測量)


Adjustment (平差)


Statistics (統計)


Wavelets (小波)


Cartography (製圖)




 








